Shook hands and kept it moving..fast forward years after his death, I read that was the first NBA game he ever attended.. Kinda cool I was
It, then Suge, Hammer, followed behind.. First time I had ever seen people react like that to seeing someone in Person. Pac just smiled
The locker room after was a sight as well. This was after he had signed with Death Row. First he walked towards the tunnel, and people LOST
This was after Magic returned to play again.. The Bulls won easy, but being a kid and watching all the celebs go thru the tunnel towards
I never met Pac, but seen him one time in person in my life. I was living in La, I had snuck into the Forum to watch the Lakers & the Bulls
Can't wait to see this Pac movie!
I thank God every single night..
